snippet.title: God of Riffs - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you ready to rock!? Boss Music Games and VYERSOFT Corp present God of Riffs: an epic, adrenaline pumping, heavy metal VR rhythm game that's like a hard rock album cover come to life!

Discord -  https://discord.gg/w75SEQ8Utb
Facebook -  https://www.facebook.com/godofriffs
Twitter -  https://twitter.com/vyersoft
Website -  https://www.godofriffs.com/

Wishlist on Steam now! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1578110/God_of_Riffs/
